&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;About you:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have the ability to build reports in Google Ad Manager and combine that data with reports from Google Analytics and other adTech platforms to form actionable insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have an understanding of best practices when it comes to placing ads on websites, with the ability to balance increasing ad revenue with maintaining site speed and user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You like to take ownership and collaborate with clients, team members, and third-party vendors to solve problems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have excellent English skills, both written and spoken, with the ability to patiently explain ad concepts to clients and team members who may have no experience with ads.&lt;/li&gt;
