&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Senior Data Analyst to help with shaping our go-to-market strategy and fueling our product growth through data-driven and actionable insights. Reporting to the Head of Data and working closely with the Growth Team, the ideal candidate requires both business acumen and technical expertise, playing a pivotal role in ensuring an efficient go-to-market strategy.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
