&lt;li&gt;Assist stakeholders in interpreting and using data for their daily tasks and provide actionable recommendations based on the analyses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct data analysis using tools like SQL, Python, Amplitude and Looker to extract meaningful patterns and relationships used to understand markets and customers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Synthesize findings and communicate them in a practical and actionable manner through visualizations and storytelling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend the reporting requirements of the organisation: from ad-hoc requests coming from the Growth Team to recurring financial and regulatory reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the quality, reliability, and accuracy of all reports and analyses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously seek ways to improve data-related processes, including report automation, data quality assurance, and advanced analytics techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
